text: Bobonaro Municipality is a municipality in East Timor. The capital city is Maliana. The Savu Sea is to the north of Bobonaro. ==Administrative posts== The municipality's administrative posts (formerly sub-districts) are: *Atabae *Balib√≥ *Bobonaro *Cailaco *Lolotoi (also spelled Lolotoe); and *Maliana. The administrative posts are divided into 50 sucos ("villages") in total. ==References== Category:Municipalities of East Timor
